Welcome Section Description
Resturent_project-3 no Class Welcome Section Design Html Css js
Today we are going to design a Welcome section of our complete Restaurant Website Template using HTML, CSS, and a little bit of JS. This tutorial is for HTML & CSS practice and through this project, we will see how can we make many things like Title Design, Image Fit,Common CSS for buttons, and how to add images, and many more things to make a complete section.

If you are thinking about what to do next after learning HTML and CSS then this tutorial would be best for you because you can do projects with them. So you need some practice for making websites and with this tutorial, you can make one of them. Therefore without any delay let's go and practice.


Although the videos are a bit long, I have prepared a time schedule for each important task for your convenience.

